Oddsmakers are expecting a tight one in this ACC match up. Can 35-year-old, first-time head coach Jon Scheyer channel some Blue Devil magic? Gametime: 7 p.m. ET TV: Live Stream: fuboTV, Sling, YouTube TV, Hulu + Live TV It was bound to start slowly for Scheyer, filling the shoes of a Duke demigod. It was going to take time for 7-foot freshman Kyle Filipowski, who has helped transform the Blue Devils into a different team during their seven-game win streak. The focus will be on the Hurricanes’ blowout win over Duke on Feb. 6, but don’t forget that Round 1 went to Duke. And don’t think these teams look anything like they did last month.